<h2> <em><dfn>Fitting a show steer</dfn></em> </h2>
<p> <strong> <dd>Fitting should be done on the day of .
Fitting your animal consist of pulling the hair up on the legs,
 As you pull the hair up on the legs with your scotch comb, spray adhesive on the hair in order to make it hold.
 Before you begin working the legs or any other body parts you must first wash and blow dry the hair thoroughly..</dd> </strong> </p>




